        <script>
        
			function resetBoxes(){
                document.getElementById("sim-per-month").value = 0;
                document.getElementById("handset-cost").value = 0;
                document.getElementById("sim-total").value = 0;
                document.getElementById("sim-monthly").value = 0;
                document.getElementById("con-per-month").value = 0;
                document.getElementById("con-handset-cost").value = 0;
                document.getElementById("con-total").value = 0;
                document.getElementById("con-monthly").value = 0;
                document.getElementById("save-total").value = 0;
                document.getElementById("save-monthly").value = 0;
			
			}
		
            function getNum(val) {
                if (isNaN(val)) {
                    return 0;
                }
               return val;
            }
        
            function calculate() {

                /* Sim only calculations*/
                // Get the values of the input boxes
                var simPerMonth = getNum(parseFloat(document.getElementById("sim-per-month").value.replace(/[^\d.-]/g, '')));
                document.getElementById("sim-per-month").value = '\xA3' + simPerMonth.toFixed(2);
                var handsetCost = getNum(parseFloat(document.getElementById("handset-cost").value.replace(/[^\d.-]/g, '')));
                document.getElementById("handset-cost").value = '\xA3' + handsetCost.toFixed(2);

                // Calculate the result
                var total = simPerMonth * 24 + handsetCost;
                var monthly = total/24;
                // Display the results
                document.getElementById("sim-total").value = '\xA3' + total.toFixed(2);
                document.getElementById("sim-monthly").value = '\xA3' + monthly.toFixed(2);

                /* contract calculations */
                // Get the values of the input boxes
                var conPerMonth = getNum(parseFloat(document.getElementById("con-per-month").value.replace(/[^\d.-]/g, '')));
                document.getElementById("con-per-month").value = '\xA3' + conPerMonth.toFixed(2);
                var conhandsetCost = getNum(parseFloat(document.getElementById("con-handset-cost").value.replace(/[^\d.-]/g, '')));
                document.getElementById("con-handset-cost").value = '\xA3' + conhandsetCost.toFixed(2);
                    
                // Calculate the result
                var total = conPerMonth * 24 + conhandsetCost;
                var monthly = total/24;
                // Display the results
                document.getElementById("con-total").value = '\xA3' + total.toFixed(2);
                document.getElementById("con-monthly").value = '\xA3' + monthly.toFixed(2);

                /* savings calculations */
                // Get the values of the input boxes
                var totalsim = parseFloat(document.getElementById("sim-total").value.replace(/[^\d.-]/g, ''));
                var totalcon = parseFloat(document.getElementById("con-total").value.replace(/[^\d.-]/g, ''));
                // Calculate the result
                var total = totalsim-totalcon;
                // Display the results
                document.getElementById("save-total").value = '\xA3' + total.toFixed(2);

                // Get the values of the input boxes
                var totalsim = parseFloat(document.getElementById("sim-monthly").value.replace(/[^\d.-]/g, ''));
                var totalcon = parseFloat(document.getElementById("con-monthly").value.replace(/[^\d.-]/g, ''));
                // Calculate the result
                var total = totalsim-totalcon;
                // Display the results
                document.getElementById("save-monthly").value = '\xA3' + total.toFixed(2);

                if(total <0){
                    document.getElementById("save-total").classList.remove('green');
                    document.getElementById("save-total").classList.remove('red');
                    document.getElementById("save-total").classList.add('red');
                    document.getElementById("save-monthly").classList.remove('green');
                    document.getElementById("save-monthly").classList.remove('red');
                    document.getElementById("save-monthly").classList.add('red');
                }else{
                    document.getElementById("save-total").classList.remove('green');
                    document.getElementById("save-total").classList.remove('red');
                    document.getElementById("save-total").classList.add('green');
                    document.getElementById("save-monthly").classList.remove('green');
                    document.getElementById("save-monthly").classList.remove('red');
                    document.getElementById("save-monthly").classList.add('green');
                }

            }
        </script>
